      "comment": "GOOSEBUMPS RICO (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (24.74) in a Grade 5 at this track. Can atone. HEART (8) was never in contention last time after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at Geelong (22.99) beating Rothwell Jack in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win on March 24. The form from her last run stacks up well. One of the better hopes. KRAKEN SCOOBY (6) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.3 lengths back in second (24.40) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 425m. Hard to beat again. DERNANCOURT (4) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
